1996年12月4日，《淘气小兵兵的光明节》在尼克儿童频道首播，并在当晚两度重播<ref>{{cite news | title = Rites of Chanukah reach many | last = Ribadeneira | first = Diego | newspaper = [[波士顿环球报|The Boston Globe]] | date = 1996-12-05}}</ref>。本集在2至11岁目标观众群收获7.9的[[尼尔森收视率|尼尔森收视率]]<ref>{{cite news | title = Nickelodeon drives kids TV marketplace in new season Grows While Competition Declines; Outperforms Broadcasters In Key Dayparts | date = 1996-12-18 | publisher = Press release, [[维亚康姆|Viacom]]}}</ref>。[[北美东部时区|北美东部时区]]2001年12月1日晚20点30分，{{lang|en|[[CBS_(电视网)|CBS]]}}电视网首度播出《淘气小兵兵的光明节》，播出时间在[[圣诞节|圣诞节]]特别节目《体验圣诞老人》（''{{lang|en|The Santa Experience}}''）之后，电视分级{{lang|en|[[美国电视分级制度|TV-Y]]}}：适合所有儿童观看<ref>{{cite news | title = Remake of 'Brian's Song' sings without excess: ; Story of friendship, love and loss still a tear-jerker; even 29 years later | newspaper = Charleston Daily Mail | date = 2001-12-01 | last = McDonough | first = Kevin}}</ref>。尼克儿童频道此后多年都在光明节期间重播本集<ref>{{cite news | title = A special Christmas from the Grinch to Spongebob, the networks are offering all sorts of holiday-themed shows | work = Albany Times Union | date = 2002-11-29 | last1 = McGuire | first1 = Mark | last2 = Wiley | first2 = Casey}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Nickelodeon's 'Ha-Ha Holidays' to Spread Chuckles and Cheer, December 5–29 | work = [[美通社|PR Newswire]] | date = 2005-11-08}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Check out holiday TV offerings | last =Elber | first = Lynn | newspaper = Post-Tribune | date = 2005-12-16}}</ref>。

《淘气小兵兵的光明节》获得电视评论员的普遍好评，是《淘气小兵兵》评价颇高的分集<ref>{{cite book | title = The Half-Jewish Book: A Celebration | last1 = Klein | first1 = Daniel | last2 = Vuijst | first2 = Freke | publisher = Villard | year = 2000 | isbn = 0-375-50385-4 | page = [https://archive.org/details/halfjewishbook00dani/page/36 36] | accessdate = 2020-07-21 | url = https://archive.org/details/halfjewishbook00dani/page/36}}</ref>。《[[芝加哥太阳报|芝加哥太阳报]]》的黛莉亚·奥赫拉（{{lang|en|Delia O'Hera}}）称赞节目是“多代同堂的传说”<ref>{{cite news | title = Holidays are a good time for family video viewing | date = 2000-12-08 | newspaper = [[芝加哥太阳报|Chicago Sun-Times]]}}</ref>。朱迪思·珀尔（{{lang|en|Judith Pearl}}）在著作《选中的影像：电视对犹太主题和人物的刻画》（''{{lang|en|The Chosen Image: Television's Portrayal of Jewish Themes and Characters}}''）中称赞本集表现光明节的方法十分有趣<ref>{{cite book | title = The Chosen Image: Television's Portrayal of Jewish Themes and Characters| last = Pearl | first = Judith | year = 1999 | publisher = [[麦克法兰公司出版社|McFarland & Company]] | isbn = 0-7864-0522-8 | page = 39}}</ref>。[[奈特·里德报业|奈特·里德报业]]和[[论坛新闻社|论坛新闻社]]（{{lang|en|Tribune News Service}}）的查克·巴尼（{{lang|en|Chuck Barney}}）认为，本集堪称“对光明节传奇的欢快想象”<ref>{{cite news | title = Other holiday programming between now and Christmas | last = Barney | first = Chuck | date = 2000-11-29 | publisher = [[奈特·里德报业|Knight Ridder]]/Tribune News Service}}</ref>。

1999年，《[[电视指南_(美国杂志)|电视指南]]》杂志发文评选“十佳经典家庭节日特别节目”，《淘气小兵兵的光明节》排名第五<ref>{{cite news | title = 10 Best Classic Family Holiday Specials | journal = [[电视指南_(美国杂志)|TV Guide]] | date = 1999-11-27}}</ref>，杂志还称，《淘气小兵兵》就是凭借这集“在电视史上拥有一席之地”，“对于任何宗教派别的孩子来说都有足够的娱乐效果”<ref name="guide" />。特德·考克斯（{{lang|en|Ted Cox}}）在《[[每日先驱报_(阿灵顿高地)|每日先驱报]]》（''{{lang|en|Daily Herald}}''）发文，认为本集虽不及之前的逾越节特别节目，但“依然值得一提”，在他看来，《淘气小兵兵的逾越节》即便是与历史上最优秀的节日电视特别节目相比也不逞多让<ref>{{cite journal | title = Seasonal all-stars The 12 top TV specials of Christmas – and other winter holidays. | last = Cox | first = Ted | date = 2005-12-01 | journal = Daily Herald}}</ref>。[[DVD谈论|DVD谈论]]（{{lang|en|DVD Talk}}）网站评论员弗朗西斯·里佐三世（{{lang|en|Francis Rizzo III}}）称赞本期特别节目“拥有伟大的历史开局”<ref name="DVD" />。迈克尔·阿特金森（{{lang|en|Michael Atkinson}}）和劳雷尔·希夫林（{{lang|en|Laurel Shifrin}}）合著的《{{lang|en|Flickipedia}}：适合在任何场合、假日、心情、苦难和起意之时观看的完美电影》（{{lang|en|''Flickipedia: Perfect Films for Every Occasion, Holiday, Mood, Ordeal, and Whim''}}）中称赞《淘气小兵兵的光明节》堪称“盛宴，对父母来说更是如此”<ref>{{cite book | title = Flickipedia: Perfect Films for Every Occasion, Holiday, Mood, Ordeal, and Whim | last1 = Atkinson | first1 = Michael | last2 = Shifrin | first2 = Laurel | page = [https://archive.org/details/flickipediaperfe00atki_0/page/12 12] | publisher = Chicago Review Press | isbn = 978-1-55652-714-2 | year = 2007 | accessdate = 2020-07-21 | url = https://archive.org/details/flickipediaperfe00atki_0/page/12}}</ref>。

=== 反诽谤联盟争议 ===
《淘气小兵兵的光明节》与其他鲍里斯爷爷和明卡奶奶出场的《淘气小兵兵》分集一样引发争议，[[反诽谤联盟|反诽谤联盟]]认为两人物设计源自20世纪30年代[[纳粹主义|纳粹]]报纸上的[[反犹太主义|反犹太主义]]绘画。身为犹太人的尼克儿童频道总裁[[阿尔比·赫希特|阿尔比·赫希特]]（{{lang|en|Albie Hecht}}）认为指控实属荒谬，对为何有人如此看待感到疑惑不解。<ref name="controversy">{{cite book | title = How The Left Lost Teen Spirit | last = Goldberg | first = Danny | year = 2005 | publisher = Akashic Books | page = [https://archive.org/details/howleftlostteens0000gold/page/216 216] | accessdate = 2020-07-21 | isbn = 0-9719206-8-0 | url = https://archive.org/details/howleftlostteens0000gold/page/216}}</ref>1998年，反诽谤联盟又针对[[犹太新年|犹太新年]]期间报纸刊登的《淘气小兵兵》[[连环漫画|连环漫画]]上鲍里斯的形象提出同样指控，并对连环画上鲍里斯朗诵[[卡迪什|犹太哀祷卡迪什]]感到冒犯。此时担任尼克儿童频道总裁的[[赫尔布·斯堪内尔|赫尔布·斯堪内尔]]（{{lang|en|Herb Scannell}}）认可批评意见并道歉，承诺不再重登这些连环画，也不再刊登任何带有鲍里斯的内容。<ref>{{cite news | url = https://www.awn.com/mag/issue3.9/3.9pages/3.9business.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200311165249/https://www.awn.com/mag/issue3.9/3.9pages/3.9business.html | deadurl = no | title = Rugrats Offends Media Watchdogs | work = Animation World Magazine | last1 = Jackson | first1 = Wendy | last2 = Amidi | first2 = Amid | date = 1998-12 | accessdate = 2020-07-21 | archivedate = 2020-03-11}}</ref>

